data.description: Charming 3/4 bedroom twin home nestled in the heart of Pottstown! This Old World gem exudes character and warmth, boasting a unique blend of charm and modern updates. The spacious living room and dining room are adorned with hardwood flooring, showcasing that timeless appeal, and the dining room features a built-in china closet. Further, sits an updated kitchen with tiled flooring, and newer appliances. Head upstairs to find a parquet wood-floored front bedroom on the second floor, radiating elegance. The remaining bedrooms boast the enduring beauty of hardwood flooring, creating a cozy and inviting atmosphere. The updated hall bathroom ensures both style and functionality for your everyday needs. Ascend to the third floor to discover an additional finished room, providing versatile space for guests, an office, or a private retreat. Embrace the outdoors from your front porch entrance to the welcoming vestibule or relax on the covered rear patio overlooking the fenced rear yard—an ideal spot for outdoor gatherings and enjoying the fresh air. Plus, the convenience of a one-car detached garage adds the finishing touch to this delightful property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this charming twin home yours. Call today!
